    <item>
      <title>Amundi、EDF 等公司要求欧盟不要削弱 ESG 规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/amundi-edf-among-firms-asking-eu-not-to-water-down-esg-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括 Amundi SA 和法国电力公司 (Electricite de France SA) 在内的一些法国最大的公司已签署了一封致欧洲政策制定者的信函，敦促他们确保欧盟坚持当前实施 ESG 报告规则的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/amundi-edf-among-firms-asking-eu-not-to-water-down-esg-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦讨论收益率上升，有望重返布鲁金斯学会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/yellen-sees-term-premium-rise-rate-repricing-behind-yield-climb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，强于预期的经济数据刺激了对利率预期的重新定价，导致美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/yellen-sees-term-premium-rise-rate-repricing-behind-yield-climb</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市挣扎，交易员为就业市场动荡做准备：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员不愿进行高风险押注，股市下跌，市场将在周五就业报告公布前夕收盘。美国国债收益率飙升，令全球投资者感到不安，之后国债价格趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚股价下跌，因警告称石油和炼油业务将影响第四季度利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/exxon-predicts-700-million-hit-to-profit-from-lower-oil-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司股价下跌，此前该公司警告称，其第四季度收益将受到 2024 年最后三个月原油价格下跌和炼油利润率收窄的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/exxon-predicts-700-million-hit-to-profit-from-lower-oil-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒冷天气导致市场紧张，英国电价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/uk-warns-of-tight-power-market-as-deep-freeze-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国电网运营商今天下午发布市场警告，由于风力发电量下降导致供应减少，而气温骤降导致需求增加，电价随后飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/uk-warns-of-tight-power-market-as-deep-freeze-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
